          {"detail": {"kind": "ServiceRequest", "status": "in-progress", "description": "Complete the full azithromycin course (5 days total). Do not skip doses even if feeling better."}},
          {"detail": {"kind": "ServiceRequest", "status": "in-progress", "description": "Use albuterol rescue inhaler as needed. Resume fluticasone/salmeterol (Advair) twice daily — do not skip."}},
          {"detail": {"kind": "ServiceRequest", "status": "in-progress", "description": "Rest and increase fluids. Expect full recovery in 1-2 weeks. Cough may persist up to 4-6 weeks — this is normal."}},
